txt.en: Your mission is to travel to Tir Katar and put an end to the caracals who have been preying on nearby travellers and help any survivors you can find.
'I thank you. The roads in the area are safe again, and I can not find the words to say how grateful the families of the survivors are to see them return home safely.'
There is no twist in this mission.
'[placeholder], your mission is to travel to Tir Katar and put an end to the caracals who have been preying on nearby travellers and help any survivors you can find.'

'Greetings, [placeholder]. Caracals have been preying on travellers near Tir Katar. I ask that you go there and put an end to these beasts to prevent further troubles.\n\n'Please keep a look out for any survivors as well and help them if you can.'
Your mission is to travel to Tir Katar and put an end to the caracals who have been preying on nearby travellers and help any survivors you can find.\n\nSpeak to Setokúli to travel.
You have successfully put an end to the caracals in Tir Katar as well as rescued any survivors! Return with the scout to Setokúli with this report.
